parameters:
How many days and nights have passed since she set out on
her journey?

I hope, for my sake, that your journey hasn't been fraught
with danger.

No, knowing you, you're probably displaying your bravery and
extending a helping hand to those in need, wherever you are.
Yes, just like you once did for me...

(Can I, like you, extend my hand to help the weak? Can I
become someone who is recognized and beloved by many, like
you are?)
What should I, powerless as I am, do...?
If only I had power like hers...

(Just as you strive to be a knight, I too must strive to be
a king... But still, I lack confidence in myself... the
confidence to care for this country...)

(Ah, even though I understand that this country is going
through a crucial time, please forgive my inadequacies...)

(Knowing that, please forgive me for escaping into such
acts...)

Thank you for listening. Please continue to enjoy the main
story.
Reisha has learned the skill "Wind Blowing to You".
